commit.message:
Teach Cucumber::Core::Test::Case to match on parent locations. (#247)

* Teach Cucumber::Core::Test::Case to match on parent locations.

This will allow it to match on lines like Feature:, Background:, and Rule:.

* ignore rubocop's complaint about long parameter list.

* ignore rubocop's complaint about too many rspec let blocks.

* refactor Core::Compiler move more low-level details into private methods.

* tighten up LocationsFilter spec nomenclature.

* update to style preference of using parens with #eq.

* rename steps for better self-documentation. the text itself doesn't actually matter.

* satisfy rubocop with dubious formatting.

---------

Co-authored-by: Micah Geisel <micah@botandrose.com>
